BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-03-29T18:15:00&endDate=2026-03-30T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWINDRUSH LINE: Sunday 29 March\, after 1915\, no service between Highbury & Islington and Battersea Park / Clapham Junction / Crystal Palace / New Cross / West Croydon. Use MILDMAY LINE services between Highbury & Islington\, Canonbury and Dalston Kingsland\, and SOUTHERN services between New Cross Gate and Crystal Palace / West Croydon.
DTEND:20260330T002900Z
DTSTART:20260329T181500Z
SUMMARY:Windrush line: Planned Closure
UID:16aaa7a7-806c-4c81-ade8-463186fa6d28@16aa.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-03-23T22:15:00&endDate=2026-03-24T01:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWINDRUSH LINE: Monday 23\, Tuesday 24\, Wednesday 25 and Thursday 26 March\, after 2215 each evening\, no service between Sydenham and West Croydon. West Croydon trains will divert to and depart from Crystal Palace instead. Use local buses or Trams via any reasonable route or Southern trains between Sydenham and Norwood Junction. Tickets will also be accepted on Southern trains between Crystal Palace and Norwood Junction\, and between Norwood Junction and East Croydon. Last through trains: Highbury & Islington to West Croydon 2202\; West Croydon to Highbury & Islington 2246
DTEND:20260324T012900Z
DTSTART:20260323T221500Z
SUMMARY:Windrush line: Part Closure
UID:07907b8d-3734-405f-8a63-7aecfafdcb27@0790.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-04-22T22:15:00&endDate=2026-04-23T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWINDRUSH LINE: Tuesday 21 and Wednesday 22 April\, after 2315 each evening\, no service between Surrey Quays and Clapham Junction / Battersea Park. Use local bus route 35 (for Denmark Hill\, Brixton\, Clapham High Street and Clapham Junction)\; bus route 37 (for Peckham Rye\, Brixton\, Clapham High Street and Clapham Junction)\; and bus route 381 (for Surrey Quays\, South Bermondsey\, Queens Road Peckham and Peckham Rye). For Wandsworth Road\, use Clapham High Street\, which is a short walk away. Last through trains: Surrey Quays to Clapham Junction 2307 (Departs Dalston Junction at 2249)\; Clapham Junction to Dalston Junction 2315
DTEND:20260423T002900Z
DTSTART:20260422T221500Z
SUMMARY:Windrush line: Part Closure
UID:0163abbc-f13c-4319-8c8f-a74fa19bf57d@0163.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-03-30T22:30:00&endDate=2026-03-31T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWINDRUSH LINE: Monday 30\, Tuesday 31 March\, Wednesday 1 and Thursday 2 April\, after 2330 each evening\, no service between New Cross Gate and West Croydon / Crystal Palace. Rail replacement buses will run as follows: the bus for Streatham Hill via Crystal Palace will depart London Bridge at 2358 calling at New Cross Gate\, Brockley\, Honor Oak Park\, Forest Hill\, Sydenham\, Crystal Palace\, Gipsy Hill\, West Norwood\, Tulse Hill and Streatham Hill. \r\n\r\nThe bus for East Croydon will depart London Bridge at 0035 calling at New Cross Gate\, Brockley\, Honor Oak Park\, Forest Hill\, Sydenham\, Norwood Junction and East Croydon. One return bus from Crystal Palace departs at 2359\, calling at all stations to London Bridge via New Cross Gate. Alternatively\, use local buses or trams via any reasonable route. \r\n\r\nLast through trains: New Cross Gate to Crystal Palace 2324\, Crystal Palace to New Cross Gate / Highbury & Islington 2332\; New Cross Gate to West Croydon 2330\, West Croydon to New Cross Gate / Highbury & Islington 2316. The 2232 and 2247 Highbury & Islington to West Croydon trains are diverted to Crystal Palace and the 2338 Dalston Junction to New Cross Gate train does not run.
DTEND:20260331T002900Z
DTSTART:20260330T223000Z
SUMMARY:Windrush line: Special Service
UID:b4791865-c09c-42d8-8322-78de0f2a2687@b479.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-03-21T04:30:00&endDate=2026-03-23T01:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nSOUTHERN: Saturday 21 and Sunday 22 March\, no service between London Bridge and Crystal Palace (via Forest Hill). Please use WINDRUSH LINE services between Canada Water\, New Cross Gate and Crystal Palace\, and JUBILEE LINE connections between London Bridge and Canada Water. An alternative train service operates between London Bridge and West Croydon (via Peckham Rye and Crystal Palace).
